title: Watch JD Crowe talk about 2 things men don't want to hear
text:
comments Watch JD Crowe talk about 2 things men don't want to hear Hearing problems J.D Crowe talks about hearing problems and a couple things men don't want to hear. Comments 
Hearing issues are common among both men and women, of course. But ladies, truth is, there are a few things us guys don't want to hear. 
A couple of them are discussed here in this Half-thunk video. Maybe y'all have more examples you'd like to get off your chest. 
You can read more snippets of nonsense in my book Half-thunk Thoughts and Half-fast Drawings.
